{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EcoThreads - Sustainable Fashion</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2c3e50;\n            --secondary-color: #34495e;\n            --text-color: #ecf0f1;\n            --accent-color: #1abc9c;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            padding: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.7), rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/2c3e50/ffffff?text=Sustainable+Fashion') center center/cover no-repeat;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #16a085;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .about-content, .collection-grid, .impact-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            align-self: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-text h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .collection-item, .impact-item {\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .collection-item:hover, .impact-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .collection-item img, .impact-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .collection-item-info, .impact-item-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .collection-item-info h4, .impact-item-info h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .collection-item-info p, .impact-item-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .impact-item-info {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .impact-item-info h4 {\n             color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .impact-item-info p {\n            color: rgba(236, 240, 241, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1rem;\n            }\n\n            section h2 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n\n            .about-content {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n\n            .collection-grid, .impact-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>EcoThreads</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#collection\">Collection</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#impact\">Our Impact</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Conscious Style, Sustainable Future</h2>\n        <p>Discover fashion that looks good, feels good, and does good for the planet. We craft timeless pieces from eco-friendly materials.</p>\n        <a href=\"#collection\" class=\"cta-button\">Shop Our Collection</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <h2>About EcoThreads</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <h3>Fashion with a Purpose</h3>\n                <p>At EcoThreads, we believe that style and sustainability can go hand in hand. We are committed to ethical sourcing, responsible manufacturing, and using innovative eco-friendly materials like organic cotton, recycled polyester, and Tencel. Our mission is to create beautiful, durable clothing that minimizes environmental impact.</p>\n            </div>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/500x400/34495e/ffffff?text=Eco-Friendly+Fabrics\" alt=\"Eco-friendly fabrics\" style=\"max-width:100%; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"collection\" style=\"background-color: #f9f9f9;\">\n        <h2>Our Latest Collection</h2>\n        <div class=\"collection-grid\">\n            <div class=\"collection-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/2c3e50/ffffff?text=Organic+Tee\" alt=\"Organic Cotton T-Shirt\">\n                <div class=\"collection-item-info\">\n                    <h4>Organic Cotton Tee</h4>\n                    <p>Soft, breathable, and made with 100% GOTS-certified organic cotton.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"collection-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/34495e/ffffff?text=Recycled+Denim\" alt=\"Recycled Denim Jeans\">\n                <div class=\"collection-item-info\">\n                    <h4>Recycled Denim Jeans</h4>\n                    <p>Classic fit jeans crafted from post-consumer recycled denim.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"collection-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/1abc9c/ffffff?text=Linen+Dress\" alt=\"Linen Blend Dress\">\n                <div class=\"collection-item-info\">\n                    <h4>Linen Blend Dress</h4>\n                    <p>Lightweight and elegant, perfect for warmer days. Made with a blend of linen and Tencel.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"impact\">\n        <h2>Our Positive Impact</h2>\n        <div class=\"impact-grid\">\n            <div class=\"impact-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/ecf0f1/2c3e50?text=Water+Savings\" alt=\"Water Savings Icon\">\n                <div class=\"impact-item-info\">\n                    <h4>Reduced Water Usage</h4>\n                    <p>Our processes use significantly less water compared to conventional fashion production.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"impact-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/ecf0f1/34495e?text=Ethical+Labor\" alt=\"Ethical Labor Icon\">\n                <div class=\"impact-item-info\">\n                    <h4>Fair Labor Practices</h4>\n                    <p>We partner with factories that ensure fair wages and safe working conditions for all employees.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"impact-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/ecf0f1/1abc9c?text=Recycling\" alt=\"Recycling Icon\">\n                <div class=\"impact-item-info\">\n                    <h4>Circular Economy</h4>\n                    <p>Committed to reducing waste through recycling and designing for longevity.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-form\">\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EcoThreads. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Made with <span style=\"color: var(--accent-color);\">&#10084;</span> for the planet.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add smooth scrolling for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}